org.apache.beam.sdk.values

Class KV<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.values.KV<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the key
    V - the type of the value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class KV<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An immutable key/value pair.

    Various PTransforms like GroupByKey and Combine.perKey(org.apache.beam.sdk.transforms.SerializableFunction<java.lang.Iterable<V>, V>) operate on PCollections of KVs.
